Invocation Name: insect repellent
des:
Disclaimer: This mosquito repeller uses ultrasonic sounds of a very high frequency which is not hearable for most people, but unbearable for mosquitos, other insects, moles, and other pests. The efficiency of this anti-mosquito sound depends on your speaker system, therefore no guarantee can be given. Please rate or review if it works, it mostly works, which depends on the capability of playing very high frequency sounds on your speaker system. You can safely play this video all night long to prevent mosquitoes from coming anywhere near you! Additionally, it is a fun app.

Enjoy.
DAILY Mosquito Repellent - 100% working ROUTINE
To add this to a daily timer, follow these steps:
1 - Open your Alexa App.
2 - Select Routines.
3 - Select Schedule, add a time (say 7 AM).
4 - Choose Skills / Your Skills.
5 - Choose 'Mosquito Repellent - 100% working'. Done.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
